  <summary>2/27/2001--Introduced.
Equity in Access to Education for Veterans Act of 2001 - Amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 (HEA) to provide, in making determinations for student financial assistance under HEA, that the amount of a student's veterans' educational benefits to be taken into consideration shall be reduced by the amount contributed from that individual's basic pay for such benefit eligibility.</summary>
